Included page: .ScenarioLibrary (edit)

These scenarios will be accessible to all test cases in the the FitNesseRoot folder. If you are using a different FitNesseRoot Folder, make sure to copy these files if using any setup scenarios.


Update these variables for your specific test environment


  • Expand
  • Collapse

Variables for Scenarios

Default browser can be FIREFOX or CHROME
variable defined: defaultBrowser=FIREFOX

Default Version can be any supported Appian Version in xx.x format from (21.2 - 23.1)
variable defined: defaultVersion=23.1

Default Locale can be en_US or en_GB
variable defined: defaultLocale=en_US

Default URL should include http or https and /suite (e.g. https://forum.appian.com/suite )
variable defined: defaultUrl=REPLACE_APPIAN_URL

To use out of the box functionality, do not update the scenarios below

  • Collapse

scenario setup for test script for browser browserType locale location version versionNum url appianUrl
setup with browser @browserType
set appian locale to @location
set appian version to @versionNum
set appian url to @appianUrl
set timeout seconds to 20
set start datetime

Raise a Request as an Employee


script
click on checkbox option [1]
populate field [2] with CSBG
wait for 5 seconds
click on radio option 1000
click on radio option 630100
populate field IO with 09 partially matching picker field suggestion
wait for 5 seconds
verify field Description[1] contains Internal order for audit purpose 3
populate field CC with 0 partially matching picker field suggestion
verify field Description[2] contains Taiwan
wait for 5 seconds
populate field Deliver To with 5th cross
populate field Building with pagsts
populate field Cube/Office/Lab Location with Banglore
wait for 5 seconds
populate grid [1] column Part Number row [1] with 0 partially matching picker field suggestion
populate grid [1] column Qty row [1] with 2
populate grid [1] column Need Date row [1] with 05/04/2023
verify button Proceed to Checkout is disabled
set take error screenshots to false
populate grid [1] column Delivery Type row [1] with Stock
wait for 5 seconds
verify button Proceed to Checkout is enabled
click on button Proceed to Checkout
populate field Short Order Description with wewrwt
wait for 5 seconds
click on button Proceed to Checkout
click on button ok
